overview:
Awe Designz is a Designing and Development firm that represents a group of professionals offering a wide range of web services.

Awe Designz service offerings span web application development, eCommerce solutions, PHP Web Development, Joomla, WordPress, Drupal, Magento, OsCommerce, ASP.Net, Yahoo Store Designing, iPhone applications development, android applications development, open source applications customizations, business and technology consulting, application services, systems integration, product engineering, custom software development, maintenance, independent testing and validation services, IT infrastructure services and hosting services.

Thanks to the technological advancement and the multi-lateral trade and agreements, the world is our playground. Thus, with proficiency, international dynamism and caliber to cope with it we play a dominant role and acquire envious competitive advantage.
